{"tid":980232,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"除左東京 京版 日本旅遊地方的推薦？","createTime":"2019-01-13T11:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T04:30:04.000Z","uid":82461,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8b868bcf730c8e112ffdb30e7cb8698f067d9a42","tid":980232,"uid":82461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T11:03:56.000Z","msg":"小弟黎緊5-6月打算同女朋友去日本畢業旅行<br />\n都去過東京 大版 唔知第三個目的地大家有咩推薦<br />\n我唔識揸車 想去5-7日 睇靚景又有d野玩下唔會太悶 <br />\n唔知大家點睇 名古屋 四國 同九洲"},{"pid":"549278fab6497e1dbb763d92fd5574cad91ffc94","tid":980232,"uid":39133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T11:04:51.000Z","msg":"仙台 廣島<br />\n可以aim睇哂日本3景"},{"pid":"58b9dda922a6d2b71d5bd4ea6b4084550be53188","tid":980232,"uid":23782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T11:08:33.000Z","msg":"好想推薦北海道 不過揸車好玩好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4550b3b32bea5967f8ba155861d92a281b2f1bcf","tid":980232,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T02:57:12.000Z","msg":"1. 大阪入，然後近鐵卷玩 京都、奈良、伊勢甚至可以玩埋名古屋，然後離開日本。<br />\n<br />\n2. 名古屋入，昇龍道直上到金沢，中途穿過下呂溫泉、高山、飛驒<br />\n3. 北九州，博多(福崗)、熊本、長崎、油布院溫泉 (千祈咪去別府地獄溫泉區，我覺得十級伏)"},{"pid":"3590cae42cb24b2771c8672b1cc33effb5947f91","tid":980232,"uid":229608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:24:42.000Z","msg":"無，香港人請盡量留在東京都、大阪府、同京都市內，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好去最好玩的北海道"},{"pid":"688395178c454f6715db66b20535dc9d67dac03e","tid":980232,"uid":28920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:28:25.000Z","msg":"山陽山陰or東北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008de35c51de7c642cad4256d2ba2d9359c226d9","tid":980232,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:29:08.000Z","msg":"尖閣"},{"pid":"9b87904b1d996c13964df767e389882e2c3609d4","tid":980232,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0